When a mother got angry, even the tiger ran away

When there is noise that the lion has come, the lion has come, everyone trembles. But this time a tiger was seen running away in fear in this viral video. A tiger was spotted attacking a herd of buffaloes in the Chandrapur Thermal Power Station area of Hua Yue, Maharashtra. The tiger even catches the smallest child of the herd and only then it happens which no one would have thought.

The calf's mother comes from behind, seeing which even the tiger runs away leaving its prey. A person has captured this thrilling war in the area of Chandrapur Thermal Power Station in the camera of a mobile phone. This video has become fiercely viral in social media
